ation”. The Federal Polytechnic is also expected to “provide technical courses of instruction and other facilities, for the pursuit of learning in all its branches, and to make those facilities available on proper terms to such persons as equipped to benefit from them”. The polytechnic when established, is expected to have powers to “establish such campuses, departments, institutes, schools, extra-mural departments, and another teaching and research units within the Polytechnic as may, from time to time, seem necessary or desirable, subject to the approval of the National Board for Technical Education, NBTE”. He added that the  “Institute Chief Lectureships, readership and associated Chief Lectureships, Lectureships and other posts and offices and to make appointments thereto”. vanguard Everyday, l trekked seven kilometres to get to my father’s farm from home to till the ground and do other things in the farm March 3, 2019 In "Politics" The Bill seeking upgrade of Federal Polytechnic, Auchi, to a university on Thursday passed second reading at the House of Representatives. March 8, 2018 In "Education" THE lawmaker representing Abi/Yakurr Federal Constituency in the House of Representatives, Dr. Alex Egbona, on Friday, revealed that the processes for the establishment of a federal polytechnic in Abi Local Government Area of Cross River State has begun, with the first reading on the floor of the House of Representatives. September 28, 2019 In "News"